name: Wesley Machiela
text: Fast service and good quality food. I ate way too much Papa Johns during college but it's still one of the better hot and ready pizza places around.

name: Tiffany Born
text: I haven't ordered from this location in a good while, only because of cutting back on spending costs, and the inconvenience of placing an order online and them denying to deliver to the house (we are 7 minutes away from the location and …More

name: Brendan caywood
text: This pizza place is very convenient. Nice for students as they can use debit dollars as well. Though the location can be a bit confusing to find. Delivery is usually fast and coupons are definitely a must for all students!

name: Drew Dobransky
text: I ordered a large boneless pizza with 3 meats on it and that pie friggin slapped. I got it A$AP and it tasted so good that it put me to sleep. 5/5

name: Nikki Abbott
text: FIX YOUR ONLINE ORDERING, HASN'T WORKED IN OVER A MONTH SO FRUSTRATING

name: Dong Pham
text: Quick and timely pizza! Worth the convenience and cost.

name: M.T. Carson
text: They call it Papa John's, but they should call Papa employees, because the employees here put their heart and soul into making you one mean pie.

name: Colin Neuman
text: Fast and friendly service. Tasty food.

name: Marcus Griffey
text: Loved getting pizza from here as an undergrad. It's easily the best Papa John's I've ever had, always fresh and able to build rewards with debit dollars!

name: Megan LaPlatt
text: Andrew Nurmi is  the best delivery driver their is. He is the bomb and deserves all the moneys. If anyone wants pizza request Andrew Nurms.

name: Alan Broene
text: The lunch special is pretty good value, don't expect much flavor though. I guess a little garlic butter would break the bottom line...

name: Nick DeRivera
text: Even when I asked for DOUBLE pepporoni they still were really stingy. The pepper they put in my pizza box looked like it had been run over. Unprofessional on the phone. This is twice now they've really disappointed me. Stick with Peppinos.

name: Courtney Bland
text: There's fine food but they don't take discover online anymore because of Aramark, and they take a while sometimes.

name: Devon Williams
text: The staff sucks... They do not answer the phone and there have been multiple times when I have walked to the location 30min. - an hour before they close and they wont let me in or serve me.

name: Jen Emerick
text: Went to order since we are driving through & haven't had dinner yet & I was I was I formed they no longer do pick up after 9pm, only delivery. Good luck keeping business with that!

name: Sam V
text:
Overall great pizza. But look at your pizza before you leave, this store seems to forget things.
Once they completely forgot to cut my pizza

name: Megan Kerin
text: Literally worst service. They won't let you use gift cards, nor will they you split the order with half cash, half card. Not even worth it to order from here. I hate this place.

name: Zach Francis
text: Used to eat lunch here all the time in between classes. If you need a quick pizza then this place will do.

name: Constance Moerland
text: Good pizza ok delivery

name: Martina Palazollo
text: The pizza is soggy... and they are very unprofessional on the phone. Don’t recommend and pizza with breadsticks was $20

name: Josiah Mazzola
text: Dont answer phone calls, dont deliver to jenison

name: Eden Lazzarini
text: They do not accept all forms of payment and the pizza didn't seem cooked all the way. Nice people though.

name: Desiree Rachwal
text: This place's food is disgusting, avoid at all costs! You will get sick like I did!

name: purechaos78
text: Friendly staff and quick service

name: Ethan Hunter
text: Donates blood, uses coupon to get a free pizza.  Expensive but SO GOOD.

name: Carlos Hernandez
text: Food is wet AF little pricy though tbh...

name: Brandon Hoffman
text: I like papa John's but this location kinda screws stuff up from time to time

name: Maria Mendoza
text: Good pizza.

name: Christoph Schuerch
text: Completely worthless pizza.

name: Dale Forton
text: Hours online are wrong!!!! So you cannot get online discounts in store WHEN it's OPEN! Manger wouldn't do it and said they are trying to get hours fixed. Do not bother with that kind of customer service.

name: Matías Gil
text: It was supposed to close 10pm(summer hours), I went at 9:20 pm and it was closed, even the employees  where inside.

name: Mike H
text: Great pizza and great service & love the pizza rewards to get free pizza

name: Savanna Pace
text: Order your pizza at least 2 hours in advance

name: Jack O'Brien
text: Their pizza just isn't good :(

name: Thomas Lynch
text:
Thhhhpppppp.

The ham was horrible
